left class=m><span class=title> Question about RANK 2.</span><hr size=1> I am very close to break 7000 Realm Points, and from what I've heard, 7200 (??) ish, is when you are awarded Rank 2. Great!<br>
What I am more concerned with, are some of the things you get when you reach Rank 2. I am wondering if these things are true.<br>
First, I was told you get a +1 to ALL your skills (stealth, CS....). However, this is NOT shown as an actual numerical change in your skill screen. So, if I have a skill level of 24 in Envenom, and am Rank2, will I be able to use level 25 poisons?<br>
<br>
There were others, but I would really like to hear what you guys KNOW for certain-- not what you've heard your best friend's mom's 2nd cousin, tell his little sister's best friend's dad. <br>
<br>
Jaax. <p><img src="http://www.flavonsen.com/images/jaax-new2.jpg">
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukeziahthotep.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Keziah Thotep</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/2/02 3:32:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2008.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about RANK 2.</span><hr size=1> Yes, the +1 bonus from Rank 2 will allow you to use a poison one higher than your actual trained skill. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usneekeerz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>sneekeerz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/2/02 4:23:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2008.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about RANK 2.</span><hr size=1> Yes, you will be able to use the lvl 25 poison with 24 envenom spec + 1 from rank. I have 28 in envenom, and +2 from rank, I can apply the lvl 30 DoT poison. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ujaaxtherogue.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jaax the Rogue</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/2/02 9:58:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2008.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about RANK 2.</span><hr size=1> VERY cool. Thanks.<br>
Anyone have a rough (or accurate) idea when we get the +2 (+3, +4...) to our skills? Is it dependent proportionaltely to our Rank? ie. Rank 2= +1.... Rank 3= +2... etc?<br>
Sneek, at how many Realm Points, did you get the +2 bonus to your skills?<br>
<br>
And if so, how many Realm Points are needed to reach each Rank (or level for the additional + to skills)?<br>
<br>
Jaax. <p><img src="http://www.flavonsen.com/images/jaax-new2.jpg">
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uciardhasidhe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ciardha Sidhe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/2/02 10:21:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2008.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.starseer.com/nightshade/ciardha60a.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about RANK 2.</span><hr size=1> What are the other perks for Rank 2?  Title?  Is Rank 2 when you start getting the messages about keeps being taken? <p><b>Ciardha Sidhe</b>, Elven Nightshade<br>Guinevere<br><small>Explorer 93% | Killer 60% | Socializer 40% | Achiever 6%</small></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umironquickblade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Miron Quickblade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/2/02 10:59:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2008.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.gwi.net/~mboutin/mirhead.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about RANK 2.</span><hr size=1> Yes, at rank two you start getting spammed when a keep gets taken. Rank three is in the 60 to 70k mark and gives a +2 to all specs. I don't believe any other benefits go with it. From what I've heard at the current time only Albion has titles. <p><table width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
