</table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ujaaxtherogue.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jaax the Rogue</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/2/02 11:46:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2008.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about RANK 2.</span><hr size=1> 60,000 Realm points for Rank 3?!! GEEZZUUUS!<br>
That's..... a LOT of time spent on raids and killing invaders!<br>
<br>
Jaax. <p><img src="http://www.flavonsen.com/images/jaax-new2.jpg">
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucaithcaidh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caith Caidh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/2/02 1:01:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2008.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about RANK 2.</span><hr size=1> Eventually, however, RPs will start rising faster, because of the RP award for a kill being based on their RPs.  As the server ages, more people will have relatively high RPs, thus the average kill will net more RPs, which bring the total that the killers are worth up a bit...  Since I've no idea how the killees RPs influences the reward, I can't guess how fast it'll rise, but it should rise to some extent at least.  Pretty soon I betcha guilds will be taking newbies out to RvR to get them to rank 2 fast for the bonus.<br>
<br>
 <p><IMG SRC="http://www.dopplex.net/sigfile2.jpg" ALT="Caith Caidh, 35th Season Nightshade, An Claidheamh Soluis" ALIGN="middle"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukeziahthotep.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Keziah Thotep</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/2/02 2:22:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2008.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about RANK 2.</span><hr size=1> Rank 3 is actually 71750 RPs <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=2008.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=2008.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2008.topic&index=8><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=2008.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.threadControl?topicID=2008.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2008.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.unsubscrib